NACC (National Alzheimer’s Coordinating Center)
Focus: Clinical and neuropathological data from Alzheimer’s centers.
Access: www.naccdata.org

Framingham Heart Study (FHS) - Neurodegenerative Component
Focus: Longitudinal cognitive and biomarker data.
Access: www.framinghamheartstudy.org

Rush Memory and Aging Project (MAP) & Religious Orders Study (ROS)
Focus: Longitudinal aging and neurodegenerative disease pathology.
Access: www.radc.rush.edu

BBRC (Barcelona Brain Research Center) Cohort
Focus: Preclinical Alzheimer’s disease research.
Access: www.barcelonabeta.org

**CSF & Biomarker Databases**
Alzheimer’s Association Global Biomarker Standardization Consortium (GBSC)
Focus: Standardization of CSF biomarkers for AD.
Access: www.alz.org/research/for_researchers/global_biomarker_standardization

BIOMARKAPD (Biomarkers for Alzheimer’s Disease and Parkinson’s Disease)
Focus: Standardized biomarker collection for AD and PD.
Access: www.neurodegenerationresearch.eu/initiatives/biomarkapd/

ABIDE (Autism Brain Imaging Data Exchange) & LEAP (Longitudinal European Autism Project)
Focus: Autism spectrum disorder but relevant for neurodevelopmental overlap with neurodegeneration.
Access: fcon_1000.projects.nitrc.org/indi/abide/

